data.description: This stately 2 story home greets you with welcoming curb appeal where upon entering, you are greeted by the formal entry. To the right of the entry is the living room, which could be used as a den or office. Through the living room, find the dining room. Through the dining room, you enter into the kitchen which is equipped with stainless steel appliances, stacked tile backsplash and abundant cabinet and counter space. Off the kitchen is the spacious and bright family room with access to the back deck. The deck walks down to the fenced in backyard with ample parking + 2 car garage. The 2nd floor features 4 bedrooms with a master suite with vaulted ceiling, walk-in closet and full bathroom. 2nd full bathroom upstairs + convenient 1st floor powder room. Enjoy strolls through the cul-de-sac and the convenience of being centrally located to the shopping, restaurants of Plum & Monroeville & easy access to the parkway & turnpike. Welcome home!
